Step 1 - Dataset Description
The dataset that we are going to use is an Online retail dataset that contains the retails store information like the Invoice number, Stock code, Description of the product, Quantity, Invoice date, Unit price, Customer ID, and Country.

Step 2 - Select Slicer
Go to the visualization pane and select the slicer to drag it onto the task window.

Step 3 - Drag and Drop the columns
Drag and drop the Invoice date column onto the Slicer

Step 4 - Make a Sample visualization
In our case, we are going to make Quantity vs Country, so when we apply slicer on it the changes were taking place.
